# Prompt-9: release outputs belong in GitHub Releases, not source control.
# APKs/AABs are large binaries that bloat the repo and the committed APK was
# unsigned — installing it directly from source is unsafe. CI publishes the
# signed AAB to Play Console; GitHub Releases hosts the signed APK for sideload.
app/release/
*.apk
*.aab
*.dm
